.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔知點同屋企人交待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抑鬱係可以靠自己走出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n解鈴還須繫鈴人 最緊要你自己點諗"},{"pid":"1e4731cad3b5b0f05f41cbdd214b0e953499b2e7","tid":263202,"uid":73805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T00:01:03.000Z","msg":"抑鬱令到重要既人都離開我 有時見到火車軌會有把聲叫我跳 今日都有 我唔想死住 搵朋友傾 結果佢已閱不回我 我又更想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49fe638beb59c829a36ea2ae8b599c92f018b6a1","tid":263202,"uid":17477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T00:02:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實覺得自己係有抑鬱<br />\n有諗過睇醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔知點同屋企人交待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抑鬱係可以靠自己走出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n解鈴還須繫鈴人 最緊要你自己點諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係咪睇心理輔導 好過食藥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930c5a4fed683ce6d05a4248f1fae975f2190872","tid":263202,"uid":83016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T00:08:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實覺得自己係有抑鬱<br />\n有諗過睇醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔知點同屋企人交待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抑鬱係可以靠自己走出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n解鈴還須繫鈴人 最緊要你自己點諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係咪睇心理輔導 好過食藥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗睇程度掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自